gate: OPEN
task: S74-TB2
title: Remove Track Get API Calls from Object History
description: |
  Remove or disable the track/get API calls that are redundant with daily endpoint:
  - Remove track/get API calls from history screen components
  - Update data fetching to use only daily endpoint
  - Remove any duplicate state management for track data
  - Ensure data transformation from daily endpoint matches UI requirements

acceptance:
  - Track/get API calls no longer appear in network tab on history screen
  - History screen displays correctly using only daily endpoint data
  - No TypeScript errors after removal
  - All history features work without track/get calls

requires: []
estimated: 4 hours
